id":2198166,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:20:13.000Z","msg":"我相信德國除左西門子之外 應該仲有好多同中共有好恐怖既勾當<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:29:37.000Z","msg":"當年納粹集中營有英美企業幫手起添"},{"pid":"359b3409eab9598a66177603077d1439c8145fca","tid":2198166,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:34:52.000Z","msg":"支持，希望多d企業轉"},{"pid":"2dd7f55c35c64bd15a1b089f1fc77992109fef7d","tid":2198166,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:39:03.000Z","msg":"德国根本係美國比壓力就屌兩句中共，中国比壓力又屌兩句美國，根本佢就唔會歸邊，有錢就得"},{"pid":"257a0008ad02a3066e38d65adf5d6dca3c9f79de","tid":2198166,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ef0e4b3062d42d1231d98e8de1b549b7a0ca9c","tid":2198166,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2dd7f55c35c64bd15a1b089f1fc77992109fef7d","tid":2198166,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:39:03.000Z","msg":"德国根本係美國比壓力就屌兩句中共，中国比壓力又屌兩句美國，根本佢就唔會歸邊，有錢就得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:54:52.000Z","msg":"No<br />\n<br />\n西門子自己本身係中國高鐵項目被洗得攤攤腰，損失慘重<br />\n<br />\n中共打完齋唔要和尚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n吸收完技術就一腳伸開佢，係海外做埋高鐵技術嘅競爭對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6fe1804df1407ae2f10ef5dfc8c2a7478848fe1","tid":2198166,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:58:05.000Z","msg":"西門子一直都敢怒不敢言，只係侵做咗爛頭卒開咗頭，班企業先敢出聲批判"},{"pid":"73d19a66aab496e6c2cc262d0